node.text: Was so lovely to meet @lailamuhammadtv from @nbc and tell them my story, how I started @nialayajewelry in a garage to opening a store on Melrose and what makes us so special ! I hope you’ll enjoy this. Happy Saturday 🌴🇺🇸 #nialaya #nbc #TV #californialive

node.text:
I did this fun TV show for Danish TV four years ago. It was a lot of fun as they followed me and my team
around, documenting how it is to live and do business in LA. Obviously very different from Denmark 🇩🇰 and then we always add a little “spice” to make it all a little more exciting. Lots of fun shooting it with very sweet people from Denmark and a lot of fun looking back at it too. Enjoy & Happy Thursday 🇺🇸🌴⚡️ #tbt #nialaya #tvshow #DanishTV

node.text: I love traveling, I love meeting new people and I love to see my family and spend time with some of my best friends in EU.  I miss it and them all the time 🙏🏼 But there is nothing like returning to LA and to my life and loved ones here. Daisy clearly felt the same way about getting her Daddy home. Doing her special little “role over & slide” at the dog park yesterday shows the Joy 🤣❤️ #backhome #LAlove @daisyolander

Unforeseen circumstances made me change my plans and extend my stay in Denmark. I spend a week on the countryside, in my brothers house (where i grew up in) alone with my mom who lives next door (through a little forest). The weather was amazing everyday and i just loved some extremely peaceful days. I can’t remember the last time I felt so grounded and relaxed. Life is unpredictable and beautiful and everything is exactly the way it’s supposed to be. Denmark is just amazing 🇩🇰❤️ Swipe left to see a few clips from my week at home #denmark #summer2021

node.text: Ping-Pong games & Rosè summer-nights in Denmark. Not a single drop was spilled 🤣🇩🇰 #pingpong #denmark #summer2021

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jannik Olander in Ibiza, Spain with @nialayajewelry, @martinhaugaard33, @inga_h1, and @jannikolander. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Ibiza it’s been real 💥
A huge thanks to my great friends for the first class hospitality. Year after year we have lots of fun, meet all our friends & create beautiful memories together. Isn’t this what life’s about ? 💙 Next stop Copenhagen ! #Ibiza #summer2021 #nialaya

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jannik Olander in Ibiza, Spain with @jannikolander. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Trying to get some rest on my last day here. Ibiza is always busy around the clock. But the magical Island never disappoints with great energy & great people 🌴❤️ #ibiza #rocalisa #summer2021

node.text: Every season is grind season and everyday is a hustle. Do you wake up late, leave your bed undone & eat shit or do you know how to switch your mindset ? Shave, shower, eat lean, kick ass at work, improve your life and mind with 1% everyday. Don’t do it for anyone else. Do it for yourself ! Because you owe yourself to be the best version you can !!! And the most important thing is to stay positive and be happy - all day everyday. Stop complaining - stop contemplating and make the changes if needed. It’s called BEAST MODE 💪🏼 Happy 4th of July everyone. Let’s GO ❤️🇺🇸🌴 #hiking #griffithpark #beastmode
